{"tid":740751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"山寨韓流！ 中國企業偽裝成南韓商店騙越南人","createTime":"2018-07-13T06:30:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T08:35:16.000Z","uid":39464,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"37afbd4fe58c3c4642cd8384587df1f8d2bde908","tid":740751,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T06:30:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/13/142839_293b6d937c37bea10fedfa9321fc02eb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F13%2F142839_293b6d937c37bea10fedfa9321fc02eb.png&h=a401b795&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國上海MUMUSO企業在越南胡志明市偽裝成南韓公司營業，店內不時播放韓流音樂，產品的標籤上也都寫著韓文，讓當地人誤以為是南韓商店，但事實上是間不折不扣的中國山寨店。<br />\n<br />\n《朝鮮日報》報導，MUMUSO並非南韓企業，總部在中國上海，商品也並非在南韓生產或產自南韓海外的工廠，已經超出山寨貨的程度，而是「山寨韓流」。<br />\n<br />\n大韓貿易振興公社（KOTRA）胡志明貿易館的相關人士認為，中國企業利用韓流在亞洲掀起的人氣，逐漸開設山寨南韓的生活綜合用品店。<br />\n<br />\n報導提到，不僅MUMUSO在胡志明市開設山寨韓流賣場，MINIGOOD和ilahui等中國企業也偽裝成南韓商店，這3間中國企業分別在全越南開設27家、15家和28家賣場。<br />\n<br />\nMUMUSO在其產品的說明書上有很小的字標示中國產和總部位於中國，目前是否合法仍不明確。胡志明貿易館的相關人士說，為避免中國企業破壞南韓商品的口碑，他們正在與越南政府協調，想出應對方案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2487095\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2487095&d=9LqqMbCbXTfEuUTDu09WMf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=6064c9dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2487095&h=401b6862\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2487095</a>"},{"pid":"55d48775c23c84dbede0816c9e1ff5d8e0420ca0","tid":740751,"uid":35430,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T07:51:02.000Z","msg":"所以話排華唔好問點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0387bf68b5702b8f419300809bfe31701013ac98","tid":740751,"uid":41116,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T08:06:59.000Z","msg":"支那企業偽裝成日本商店騙香港人"},{"pid":"a4ca2bac403b6d5253c4a8235b4877535aa6770f","tid":740751,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T08:07:50.000Z","msg":"支那野賣唔出咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e8ada5a83179e555d7b223d3f2d844f72028763","tid":740751,"uid":129169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T08:13:54.000Z","msg":"香港都有間mini啦，大把人買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5fe34162cb1e82112b5bf947c29085e1c6fb8d4","tid":740751,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T08:14:29.000Z","msg":"老老實實,中國人要扮韓國人嘅話其實好難分得到,因為韓國人咪又係中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06492c0c9c9d08b67841e3d95ef19ca9f3bbbda0","tid":740751,"uid":19353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T08:35:16.000Z","msg":"其實扮都冇用 入過呢d店睇 貨品質素真係好差又貴 呃唔到人"}]}